#~ "project.org/doc/qt-4.8/qt.html#Key-enum\">Qt documentation</ulink> for "
#~ "further details."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<literal>a.shortcut</literal> [optioneel]: De hier gegeven sneltoets is "
